Music - Shamur
Lyrics - LSL

Lyrics🙏
Te.ri.. chhaya.. mein...
te.re.. charno... mein..
Magan, ho, bai.thu..
te.re, bhakto.. mein..

Tere, darbaar mein, maiya
khushi, milti, haii
Tere, darbaar mein, maiya
khushi, milti, haii
zindagi, milti hai,
roto ko
hasi milti hai
Tere darbar mein, maiya
khushi, milti, haii

Ek, ajab si, masti
tan mann..pe, chhati hai
Har ek, jubaa tere, o maiya
geet, gaati, hai
Baj.te, sitaro se
mee.thi, pukaro se
Goonje, jahan, saara
tere, unche, jai kaaro se
Masti mein jhumein
tera dar chume
Tere chaaro.. taraf
duniya, ye ghume
Aisi masti bhi, bhala kya

kahin, milti hai
zindagi, milti hai,
roto ko
hasi milti hai
Tere, darbaar mein, maiya
khushi, milti, haii

meri, shero, waali maa
teri, har baat, achchhi hai
Karni ki, poori hai
maata, meri, sachhi haii
Sukh dukh bataati hai
apna banaati hai
Mushkil, mein ho, bachche
to maa hi, kaam aati hai
Raksha karti.. hai
bhakt apne.. ki
Baat, sachchi, krti
unke sapno.. ki
Saari duniya ki, dau.lat

yahin, milti hai
zindagi, milti hai,
roto ko
hasi milti hai
Tere, darbaar mein, maiya
khushi, milti, haii

Rota hua, aaye jo
hasta hua, jata hai
Mann, ki.. muraado ko
wo, paa.taa hua, jaata haii
Kismat ke, maaro ko
rogi, bimaaro ko
Kar de, bhala changa,
apne. dulaaro, ko
Paap, kat, jaaye
charan chhune se
Meh.kti, hai duniya
maa ke dhune se
Fir tu, maa..
aisi, kabhi, kya
kahin milti hai
zindagi, milti hai,
roto ko
hasi milti hai

Tere, darbaar mein, maiya
khushi, milti, haii
